{"tid":25206,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"南美足協正式宣佈 查比高恩斯獲南美盃冠軍","createTime":"2016-12-06T03:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T12:01:59.000Z","uid":33730,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"228b070fb5ba84ae87dd7481c914d834d01aba6e","tid":25206,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"〔體育中心／綜合報導〕南美足球協會今天正式宣佈，日前因墜機意外幾乎全隊喪生的巴西球隊查比高恩斯獲得南美盃冠軍，對手哥倫比亞國民競技則獲頒百年公平競賽獎。<br />\n<br />\n查比高恩斯原本將在週三出戰國民競技，進行南美盃決賽第一戰，不過卻搭上失事班機，「22名球員、28名隨行與訓練員、22名記者與9名職員」在美德殷郊區墜機罹難。<br />\n<br />\n國民競技在得知消息後發表聲明表示哀悼，同時向南美足協要求將冠軍追贈給巴西對手以表尊敬，今天南美足協正式宣佈將南美盃冠軍頒給查比高恩斯。<br />\n<br />\n國民競技獲得亞軍，以及南美足協頒發的百年公平競賽獎與100萬美元獎金，表彰其令人欽佩的運動家風度。<br />\n<br />\n南美足協表示，受難的查比高恩斯獲得冠軍外，還將享有未來參賽保證以及經濟上的協助。<br />\n<a href=\"http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1908497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F1908497&d=t4UGmyAz6k58H4TqneELPgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=61de8270\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F1908497&h=eb1b8f49\" target=\"_blank\">http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1908497</a>"},{"pid":"ba8feda083f4aa2d6dc4c17d02c3666b27558acd","tid":25206,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4590cf5b4e1e313b13fb5ea811af0a5bb8e36579","tid":25206,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.conmebol.com/sites/default/files/chaoe-campeon-750px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.conmebol.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fchaoe-campeon-750px.jpg&h=d35725a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b90c7ab51f651e6b00b67aea0f007835aed0b79","tid":25206,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:40:55.000Z","msg":"人生如夢"},{"pid":"5ea074da1483beae