ced8759eedb68fcda01f4da9ec5ea71b4a3","tid":25206,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今屆取消咪算, 比個冠軍佢地 仲痛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n球會第一個南美冠軍係陷隊產......."},{"pid":"96a155b5579f80a517b53411eef251a988507113","tid":25206,"uid":48604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"雙贏既決賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb35b191f7d6fc3476d2cbbdbb9c3e904767d21d","tid":25206,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:14:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冠軍係咪有南美自由盃打？得返青年軍同巴甲借將點應付雙線作戰</blockquote><br />\n下屆要打南美自由盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細哨"},{"pid":"72b31b075194389c919ba598b71a4251f1eb07ce","tid":25206,"uid":1991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:26:05.000Z","msg":"咁買左佢冠軍有得收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw     RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0df74057cacd3eef7f2b4d49c7191a20180ca66","tid":25206,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁買左佢冠軍有得收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw     RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n南球盃決賽踢唔成 馬會識做兩邊派彩<br />\n<br />\n馬會今日宣佈，根據南美足協的決定，下注了查比高恩斯為南美球會盃冠軍將獲得派彩，另外由於情況特殊，足智彩亦會向下注國民體育會為南球盃冠軍的作出酌情派彩。<br />\n<br />\n由於巴甲球會查比高恩斯上周一在前赴哥倫比亞準備參加南球盃決賽首回合時遇上空難，比賽被逼無限期延期，而查比的決賽對手國體會主動要求南美足協將冠軍頒予查比，南美足協亦已在周一正式宣佈查比為今屆南球會盃冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20161206/56011124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20161206%2F56011124&d=t4UGmyAz6k58H4TqneELPgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=9bbb4470\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20161206%2F56011124&h=c1247fe3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20161206/56011124</a>"}]}